FrmAndLnRfrncDsc: Schedule K, Part I, Column f-02/25/2005 45,500,000 Massachusetts Development
ExplntnTxt: The proceeds of the Bonds loaned to ISO New England Inc. were made to finance and refinance a project located at One Sullivan Road, Holyoke, Massachusetts; generally consisting of (a) the acquisition of a 13-acre parcel of property and attached existing 64,000 square foot facility; (b) the renovation, equipping and furnishing of the existing facility, including construction of a 3,200 square foot expansion, a new lobby and mechanical penthouses, (c) construction, equipping and furnishing of a three story, 100,000 square foot facility; and (d) construction of site Improvements, including but not limited to an additional 342-space parking lot, a retaining wall and security screen, a pedestrian connecting bridge between the existing and new facility and a guard house, all to be used by the company to conduct its mission and activities.

FrmAndLnRfrncDsc: Schedule K, Part I, Column f-12/13/2012 36,000,000 Connecticut Innovations Incorporated
ExplntnTxt: The proceeds of the Bonds loaned to ISO New England Inc., were made to (i) finance the cost of (a) acquisition of real property located at 55 Helmsford Way, Windsor, Connecticut (the "Property"), (b) the construction of an approximately 70,000 square foot office building for a Back-up Control Center with data center and control room components on the Property, (c) the purchase and installation of general machinery, equipment, office furniture and fixtures and (d) miscellaneous capital projects; and (e) pay costs of issuance and credit enhancement fees with respect to the Bonds (the "Project").
